{"title":"找书记","authors":["余开来"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":10,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"找书记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"余开来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前天我去找书记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记正在看图纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸上画的土高炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中拿的米突尺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天又去找书记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记挂帅在工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍刀碰得叮咚响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满身满脸都是泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天再去找书记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记炉前看风力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗啦一下炉门开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众欢呼迎铁水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书记挂帅插红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万英雄来结集，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比巨龙乘东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万座高炉平地起。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}